<%- include('partials/header') %>

<div class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-overlay"></div>
  <div class="page-hero-content">
    <h1>Frequently Asked <span>Questions</span></h1>
    <p>Find answers to the most common questions</p>
    <nav class="breadcrumb">
      <a href="/">Home</a> <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i> <span>FAQ</span>
    </nav>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="section faq-section">
  <div class="container faq-container">
    <div class="faq-intro">
      <span class="section-tag">FAQ</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Your Questions <span>Answered</span></h2>
      <p>Can't find your answer here? <a href="/contact">Contact our team</a> and we'll be happy to help.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-categories">
      <div class="faq-category">
        <h3><i class="fas fa-car"></i> Test Drives</h3>
        <div class="faq-list">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">Can I take a test drive before buying?<i class="fas fa-plus"></i></button>
            <div class="faq-answer"><p>Absolutely. We strongly encourage test drives — we believe you should never buy a car without experiencing it on the road first. Simply <a href="/appointment">book an appointment</a> or call us to arrange a test drive at a time convenient for you. All we ask is that you bring a valid driving licence.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">How long is a typical test drive?<i class="fas fa-plus"></i></button>
            <div class="faq-answer"><p>Our test drives typically last 20–40 minutes, covering both urban and open road conditions so you can experience the vehicle in real driving scenarios. Our team member will accompany you and answer any questions during the drive.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">Do I need to make an appointment for a test drive?<i class="fas fa-plus"></i></button>
            <div class="faq-answer"><p>We recommend booking in advance to ensure the vehicle is ready and our team can give you their full attention. However, we do welcome walk-ins when our schedule allows. Call us at +355 69 123 4567 to check availability.</p></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-category">
        <h3><i class="fas fa-euro-sign"></i> Pricing & Finance</h3>
        <div class="faq-list">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">Are the prices negotiable?<i class="fas fa-plus"></i></button>
            <div class="faq-answer"><p>Our prices are set competitively and reflect the true market value of each vehicle. We price fairly from the start, so you won't need to negotiate hard. However, we are always happy to discuss options, particularly when it comes to part-exchange or bundled services.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">Do you offer financing options?<i class="fas fa-plus"></i></button>
            <div class="faq-answer"><p>While we don't directly provide financing, we work with trusted banking partners in Albania and can refer you to financial institutions that offer competitive auto loan rates. Our team can guide you through the financing process and help you understand your options.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">Can I pay in installments?<i class="fas fa-plus"></i></button>
            <div class="faq-answer"><p>This depends on your financial institution and the terms agreed. We can help facilitate discussions with our partner banks regarding installment payment plans. Please speak with our team for more information.</p></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-category">
        <h3><i class="fas fa-search"></i> Vehicle Inspection</h3>
        <div class="faq-list">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">Do your vehicles come with an inspection report?<i class="fas fa-plus"></i></button>
            <div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes. Every vehicle in our inventory undergoes a thorough 150-point mechanical and cosmetic inspection by our certified technical team. We are happy to share the full inspection report upon request.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">Can I have the car independently inspected?<i class="fas fa-plus"></i></button>
            <div class="faq-answer"><p>Absolutely — we welcome independent inspections. We have nothing to hide and encourage buyers to have full confidence in their purchase. You can arrange an inspection with a trusted mechanic of your choice. We'll work around your schedule to make this possible.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">How can I check the vehicle history?<i class="fas fa-plus"></i></button>
            <div class="faq-answer"><p>We provide full documentation history for every vehicle, including service records, previous ownership documents, and import papers where applicable. We can also assist you in running an official vehicle history check.</p></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-category">
        <h3><i class="fas fa-bookmark"></i> Reservation & Purchase</h3>
        <div class="faq-list">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">Can I reserve a vehicle?<i class="fas fa-plus"></i></button>
            <div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes. We can hold a vehicle with a reservation deposit while you finalise your decision or arrange financing. A reservation removes the car from sale temporarily and gives you peace of mind. Contact us to discuss terms.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">What paperwork is included with the purchase?<i class="fas fa-plus"></i></button>
            <div class="faq-answer"><p>We provide a full sale contract, vehicle registration transfer documents, all available service history, technical inspection certificates, and any import/export documentation. Our team handles the paperwork to make the process as smooth as possible.</p></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">Do you accept part exchange?<i class="fas fa-plus"></i></button>
            <div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes, we consider part exchange on a case-by-case basis. Bring your current vehicle for an assessment and we can discuss how it might contribute toward your next purchase. The value offered depends on the condition, age, and demand for your vehicle.</p></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-cta">
      <h3>Still have questions?</h3>
      <p>Our team is always happy to help. Reach out through any channel.</p>
      <div class="faq-cta-btns">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary"><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Send a Message</a>
        <a href="/appointment" class="btn btn-outline"><i class="fas fa-calendar"></i> Book Appointment</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
document.querySelectorAll('.faq-question').forEach(btn => {
  btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
    const item = btn.closest('.faq-item');
    const isOpen = item.classList.contains('open');
    document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item').forEach(i => i.classList.remove('open'));
    if (!isOpen) item.classList.add('open');
  });
});
</script>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
